    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <date>Mon</date>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <date>June 1, 1857</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <hi rend="underline">
                    <add>Hebrew</add>
                </hi>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(center)"><placeName>Buffalo</placeName>, <date>8<hi rend="sup">th</hi>
                    Sivan, 1857</date></p>
            <p rend="align(center)">(<date>June</date>)</p>
            <p>To my dearest friend, Sweet-singer of <placeName>Israel</placeName>,<lb/> etc.
                etc.</p>
            <p>Dear friend,</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I <del>am not</del> have no intention to burden<lb/> you with words,
                but only to reveal to you<lb/> what I saw yesterday when I was at the<lb/>
                Synagogue. Half the books that used to be<lb/> there are stolen, and there are left
                for you<lb/> only a very small number. Only the Bible<lb/> is still to be found. The
                rest are gone forever.<lb/> The Hazan, who lives there, told me that he<lb/> has
                found only these. He had come to <placeName>Buffalo</placeName><lb/> after
                    <date>Passover</date>, and does not know who took<lb/> the rest of the books.
                Therefore, I want to<lb/> ask you what to do if any people should<lb/> want to
                purchase the rest cheap. Shall I<lb/> sell or not. There is no further news. I<lb/>
                expect a clear answer soon.</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)"><persName role="author">Yitshok Itzik</persName> son of
                    <persName>Moses Slatky</persName></p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">The Address</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <persName>Isaac M. Slattkey</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <placeName>Box 2648</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <placeName>Buffalo N. Y.</placeName>
            </p>
        </body>
